snippet.title: Stella Sora Concept PV「To the endless sky」
snippet.description:
Where yearns the heart, endless possibilities await.
The unknown beyond the wall beckons, and someone must step into the wild to answer its call.
"If someone knocks on this door, the world would surely change."

Trekkers bravely ascend the Monoliths with you by their side. This is your story.
Tales of love and hope await.

——
Stella Sora Concept Image Song 「To the endless sky」
Song: Isekaijoucho
Lyrics: Rui Kohara
Music: Shigenobu Okawa
Arrangement: Kent Asahina

——
Pre-registration is now available for Stella Sora on our official website!
